		"Dr. Mario
	]em
	" than the original 
	[em 
		"Tetris
	]em
	" in that the goal is to match the colors of the descending tetrominoes with pre-positioned blocks on the play field. When three or more blocks of the same color line up, they are eliminated. When three or more blocks are lined up with the special flashing blocks, 
	[em 
		"all
	]em
	" blocks of that color are eliminated at once.
